timeline.bodyText:
Do we need to add a DocService test?
I think we can test the Period converter by registering an annotated service that takes a Period as a @Param and calling it by a WebClient.
For example:



      armeria/core/src/test/java/com/linecorp/armeria/internal/server/annotation/AnnotatedServiceRequestConverterTest.java


        Lines 917 to 923
      in
      52fd361







           @Test 




           void testDefaultRequestConverter_uuid() { 




               final WebClient client = WebClient.of(server.httpUri()); 




               final UUID uuid = UUID.randomUUID(); 




               final AggregatedHttpResponse response = client.get("/2/default/uuid/" + uuid).aggregate().join(); 




               assertThat(response.contentUtf8()).isEqualTo(uuid.toString()); 




           }

